  audioClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9dc5d5a0ea7b61044b5e02730d0ec82c, type: 3}
  message: "Welcome onboard Lieutenant, I trust Sergeant Jenkins has given you a
    thorough rundown of today\u2019s itinerary. Let\u2019s begin quickly and let\u2019s
    move fast. Today we\u2019ll be expecting bombardments in the marked artillery
    zone C-21. Stand by for my command and do not enter the zone without target confirmation.
    I repeat, do not enter the zone without target confirmation, only enter when
    you do have confirmation directly from me. Looking forward to thrashing these
    rapscallions for good. Cheerio. Over and out."
